        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Debt Ceiling Reform Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Secretary of the Treasury to increase the public debt limit. Under current law, the debt limit restricts the amount of funds that the Department of the Treasury may borrow to fund the federal government. </p>]]>
        </text>
